Love Heals has been planting 10 trees for each design sold since 2007. To date over 700,000 trees have been planted.

When you purchase a Love Heals jewellery piece you have made it possible to plant another 10 trees. Other charities they sponsor for each item sold protect 8 children who might have lost their sight from vitamin deficiency, or make a difference in a child’s life who’s struggling with the difficulties of living with autism. 

Made in USA.

name: Love Wrapped
description:
This "love" piece can be worn as a long necklace or a bracelet.
The sterling silver pendant is on a natural toned waxed polyester cord.

To wear as a bracelet: pull slip knot away from the pendant to create a small loop that fits around wrist, continue to pull slip knot close to wrist until tight and comfortable. Wrap remaining string around wrist and tuck pendant under string a few times to secure. Tie a knot to keep bracelet secure.

To wear as a necklace: pull slip knot toward the pendant to create a large loop and slip over neck to wear as a long necklace.

It comes packaged in small glass vial.

The pendant size is about 6mm (0.25").
The cord is about 76cm (30").

Made in USA.

name: Lelite Soap
description:
The Lelite soaps distinguish themselves due to the combination of the fruity aroma of the extracts of Sicilian oranges, with remnants of the sweet and warm amber. 

Daring in smell, but delicate in the characteristics, these soaps provide a relaxing and antioxidant effects while hydrate and successfully protect the skin.  

The ingredients are 100% natural and the recipe dates back to 1887. The soap is vegetable based with a concentrated shea butter formula which is milled seven times so that there is no cracking or splitting.

350g (12.4 oz).

Made in Portugal.

name: Rivale Soap
description:
If the soul of the Rivale soaps is in the essential grapefruit oil, whose anti-septic and restoring characteristics are specific for the care of oily skins, the personality of these products can be found in the penetrating, bitter aroma of the grapefruit and in the wooden sweetness of the mature figs.

From this fruity mixture of smells results an intense but balanced fragrance, with a mysterious touch of exoticism.

The ingredients are 100% natural and the recipe dates back to 1887. The soap is vegetable based with a concentrated shea butter formula which is milled seven times so that there is no cracking or splitting.

350g/12.4 oz.

Made in Portugal.

name: Lilane Soap
description:
The Lilane soaps are produced from lavender essential oil, they are fresh, cheerful, intense and have a lasting perfume. The pure, aromatic fragrance and the relaxing, calming action of the lavender provide a lasting sensation of well-being, completed with the anti-septic effect that it also assures.

Besides disinfecting, the Lilane soaps clean the skin deeply without drying, they hydrate and protect the skin, leaving it radiant during the whole day.

The ingredients are 100% natural and the recipe dates back to 1887. The soap is vegetable based with a concentrated shea butter formula which is milled seven times so that there is no cracking or splitting.

350g/12.4 oz.

Made in Portugal.

name: My Life Story
description:
A 100 year diary for you to record the events of a lifetime. It will help you to remember the special moments you will never want to forget... the people you have loved, the friends you have made, the places where you have lived and those you have travelled to. You can record your achievements as well as your skills, make a note of favourite films/books/music/people and write down all your ambitions and things you want to do before you die. A map of the world and one of your body is included and can be filled in as you choose.

If you are too young to fill it in right now someone else can  fill it in for you, things like your first steps, first words and first day at school...What a beautiful gift to start for your son or daughter!

This is the story of your life, treasure it always.

1080 pages
The journal measures 16.3 x 22.7 x 6.8 cm (6.4"x8.9x2.6").

name: Oak Tree Print
description:

This is an archival print of an original pen and ink drawing by Paula Mills. The patterns are delicate with detail. Each print is produced by high quality ink jet, using archival inks, on matte heavyweight, bright white card, which is signed and dated by the artist.

The actual artwork is A5, it measures approximately 13cm x 18cm (5" x 7"). A white border will be left for framing.

name: Camille Set
description:
Here is Camille!

This set includes a tiny pocket doll in a matchbox house and a sixteen page booklet full of unique black and white illustrations by Paula Mills ready for you to color as you wish.

Camille lives in a matchbox doll house with her budgie friend or her cuckoo clock and she dreams about all her adventures. She dreams of talking to elephants, riding with swans in the moonlight and flying with angels. She loves to hear about your dreams too. She is hand stitched on to felt, slightly stuffed, and sits neatly in her house.

In the colouring book Camille is dancing with the wind, swinging from trees, laughing, hugging elephants, flying with angels, floating in tea cups and much, much, more! 

The house measures approximately 5cm (2").
The booklet measures approximately 21cm x 15cm ( 6" x8.25").

Handmade in Australia.
